  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for the Night Time Economy",
  "purpose": "To provide a cross-party voice to champion nightlife’s cultural and economic importance. To promote policy opportunities and solutions, working in partnership with cross-sector stakeholders. To support and unlock equitable growth through the Night Time Economy (NTE). To protect and support NTE spaces and ecosystems from immediate threats.",
